    "18391363": {
      "title": "In-memory graph databases for web-scale data",
      "abstract": "A software stack relies primarily on graph-based methods to implement scalable resource description framework databases on top of commodity clusters, providing an inexpensive way to extract meaning from volumes of heterogeneous data."
